de.unibox.client.thread

Class ThreadEngine

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.unibox.client.thread.ThreadEngine

  • public class ThreadEngine
extends java.lang.Object
    The Class ThreadEngine is responsible for all worker threads. It provides a pool to get rudimentary access and control to all available worker threads.
